HEADWORD: ostracod
<hw>ostracod</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A member of the
<ord>Ostracoda</ord>, an order of tiny marine and freshwater crustaceans
with a shrimplike body enclosed in a bivalve shell.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> seed shrimp, mussel shrimp.</syn>⟦br⟧
